Features able to complete:
1. Each disk is a rectangle. All disks have the same widths, but have different lengths.
2. Each disk is of a different color
3.  a 	start with all the disks on the left tower and end with all the disks on the right tower
	b 	animate each step of the solution
	c 	show disks flying between towers one at a time
	d 	Once the solution is complete, 
		users are able to press Space bar to restart the visualization 
		without having to run the program again
4. Take the number of disks as a command-line argument; check for invalid arguments

Extra1: able to change from autoMode to keyMode
	Press A for AutoMode; 
	Press D for KeyBoardMode; 
	Press SPACE for move under KeyBoardMode